parcel.description:
欢迎光临复兴工厂。在22世纪，人类已无须桎梏于肉身，寄生于AVATAR在元宇宙中继续生活。同时，人类又生产着数量庞大的AI，为了给AVATAR提供更好的服务。所有的AVATAR与AI皆为批量生产，而输出他们的复兴工厂成为了未来世界的基本运作单位。

Welcome to Fuxing Factory. In the 22nd century, evolved human beings upload consciousness to the Cloud and parasitizing in avatars, continue their lives in metaverse. At the same time, huge amount of AI has been made to provide service for human avatars. All avatars and AI are mass produced by Fuxing Factory, a basic manufactory unit in the future world.
